<body id="about-page" class="background-transition">
    <!-- @include "global/header_nav.kit" -->

    <main >
        <section class="intro-type">
            <div aria-hidden="true" class="small-square"></div>
            <div class="paragraph-container">
                <div>
                    <div aria-hidden="true" class="small-square"></div>
                    <div aria-hidden="true" class="small-square"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="semibold-24pt">Creativity can strike<br>at any moment<br><br><br>Sometimes the best<br>ideas are scribbled on<br>a <span class="txtbold">dirty napkin</span></h1>
        </section>

        <section class="hero-image">
            <div class="vimeo-video hero-image" style="--poster:url('assets/vimeo-thumbnails/a1d.jpg');padding:74.06% 0 0 0;">
                <iframe 
                    src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1146807030?background=1&autoplay=1&loop=1&muted=1&controls=0" 
                    frameborder="0" 
                    allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture;" 
                    title="A1D_team-photo">
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="approach">
            <div class="story-title">
                <h2>approach</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p>
                The three of us met in college and quickly bonded over an ambition for our design work. We started Dirty Napkin out of an eagerness to do work for clients we cared about.
            </p>
            <p>
                We approach each of our design projects with that same eagerness and a desire to build unique worlds that understand and elevate our clients’ missions. This is done through custom brand strategy and relentless iteration.
            </p>
            <h2 aria-hidden="true">approach</h2>
        </section>

        <section class="services">
            <div class="services-bar top semibold-24pt" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <h2 class="semibold-24pt">Services</h2>
            <!-- <div class="video-container"> -->
                <div class="vimeo-video" id="A5M" style="--poster:url('assets/vimeo-thumbnails/a5m.png');padding:7.03% 0 0 0;">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1146810957?background=1&loop=1&muted=1&controls=0" 
                        frameborder="0" 
                        allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture;" 
                        title="a5m_services-list">
                    </iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="vimeo-video-two">
                    <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                    <div class="vimeo-video" id="A5D" style="--poster:url('assets/vimeo-thumbnails/a5d.png');padding:110% 0 0 0;">
                        <iframe 
                            src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1146810947?background=1&loop=1&muted=1&controls=0" 
                            frameborder="0" 
                            allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture;" 
                            title="a5d_services-list">
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="vimeo-video left" id="A6" style="--poster:url('assets/vimeo-thumbnails/a6.png');padding:60% 0 0 0;">
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1146810967?background=1&loop=1&muted=1&controls=0" 
                        frameborder="0" 
                        allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture;" 
                        title="a6_puzzle-type">
                    </iframe>
                </div>
            <!-- </div> -->
            <div class="services-bar bottom semibold-24pt" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="two-prongs">
            <h2 class="semibold-32pt">We love what we do</h2>
            <h2 class="semibold-32pt">and brand design is just the beginning</h2>
            <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p>
                Strong branding is necessary to establishing a community that is built on trust, personality, and loyalty. We believe in empowering the small do-ers with the same visual toolkit that the big leagues get. 
            </p>
            
        </section>

        <section class="team">
            <div class="team-header">
                <!-- <h2>Founded by Students <br> in 2023</h2> -->
                <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div class="small-square" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-members">
                <div>
                    <img src="assets/about-pg/A4_nick-headshot.jpg" alt="Nicholas Evangelinos">
                    <h3>Nick Evangelinos</h3>
                    <p>is our Designer and Head of Growth. Art imitates life; life imitates Nick.<br>
                        <span class="awards">GDUSA Award Winner</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="assets/about-pg/a2_evan-headshot.jpg" alt="Evan Whitaker">
                    <h3>Evan Whitaker</h3>
                    <p>is our Designer and Brand Strategist. He is a figment of our imagination.<br>
                        <span class="awards">GDUSA Award Winner</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="assets/about-pg/A3_dan-headshot.jpg" alt="Dan Soslowsky">
                    <h3>Dan Soslowsky</h3>
                    <p>is our Designer and Project Manager. He once saw a shark and wasn’t scared even a little bit.<br>
                        <span class="awards">GDUSA Award Winner</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </section>

        <section class="mission">
            <div class="story-title">
                <h2>Mission</h2>
            </div>

            <p>
                We want to make the world as exciting as possible. And to make our moms proud. Good ideas will only ever get out if someone has the grit to pursue them. We push our clients to experiment with bold ideas and exciting graphics because we are committed to giving it our all, and you better be too. 
            </p>
            <p>
                If you are a heartfelt business, an independent creator, or a cute dog looking to become the Dirty Napkin company pet, we want to hear from you.
            </p>

            <a href="mailto:hello@dirtynapkin.co" class="button-text hover-style-one">Contact Us</a>
            <h2 aria-hidden="true">Mission</h2>
        </section>

        <section class="logo-row" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="assets/logomark.svg" alt="" class="logo-repeat">
                <img src="assets/logomark.svg" alt="" class="logo-repeat">
                <img src="assets/logomark.svg" alt="" class="logo-repeat">
                <img src="assets/logomark.svg" alt="" class="logo-repeat">
            </div>
        </section>
